Julienne Mathieu https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julienne_Mathieu 0 Julienne Mathieu was one of the earliest French silent film actresses who appeared mostly in French silents between 1905 and 1909. She appeared in the Spanish silent film El Hotel eléctrico released in 1908, one of the first films to incorporate stop animation.
